data.description: Imagine unwinding after a bustling day in the city, stepping into the serenity of your exquisite lakeside retreat on Lake Talquin. Picture yourself on the covered porch, savoring the sunset or embarking on an evening cruise from your very own boat dock. Allow me to introduce you to the epitome of lakefront living – a meticulously crafted 2022 modular home that's not only beautiful but also move-in ready.  Nestled on nearly half an acre, this residence boasts a private boat dock with a lift, cleaning station, and storage for all your aquatic gear. Featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this 1,650 sq ft haven is an oasis of modern luxury. Every inch of this home is 2019 and newer, including a perfectly situated above-ground pool with surrounding decking view a perfect view of the nature and lake.  Step into the primary suite and discover a spacious walk-in closet alongside a lavish bathroom equipped with a double sink vanity, shower, and a free-standing garden tub beckoning for a tranquil soak as well as full shower. The kitchen, designed with an open concept, is an entertainer's delight. New appliances, stylish accents, and an inviting island make it the perfect space for both preparation and gathering, ensuring you never miss out on the festivities. Surrounded by a fully fenced yard with an electric entrance gate, this property includes a fresh storage unit and a new concrete driveway leading to a carport capable of accommodating three vehicles. This home is so new, there is still personal items in boxes.  Act now, as a property of this caliber at this price is a rare find that won't last long!
